Bethlehem Steel Corp said itsbase price for carbon plates and high-strength and low-alloyplates will be increased by 25 dlrs to 405 dlrs a short ton,effective July one.    The company said its composite prices for alloy plates willalso be increased 25 dlrs per ton on the same date, adding itdoes not publish its prices for this product.    Bethlehem Steel said its composite prices for strip millplates will be increased 15 dlrs a ton. Reuter&#3;